{"tid":1473826,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家真係要睇下大陸清醒人士的說法","createTime":"2019-08-15T03:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T03:59:11.000Z","uid":216779,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"64339ea3d081b5d135de29790540e0a17117e15a","tid":1473826,"uid":216779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:15:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">至從有巴打上傳左致大陸同胞書返大陸，我都一直去留意內地清醒人士對香港呢兩個月既事有咩睇法<br />\n佢地係極度支持同希望香港人可以成功！！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">對於翻牆人士黎講，邪惡中共既高壓管治手段真係十惡不赦，亦有網友話比起燒國旗，燒黨旗會令更多大陸人有同感和支持！因為不少大陸人都只愛國，并非愛黨，佢地係牆內生活，非常明白中共既邪惡，比起我地更加心知肚明，卻無力改變同反抗</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ASGsVLc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FASGsVLc.png&h=b1263a37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FnSS6R8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFnSS6R8.png&h=a09536f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">實際上五毛都係比<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中共洗腦既可憐蟲</span></strong>，根本無需要浪費時間同佢地爭辯，但我地必須要記得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將更多革命性訊息帶比清醒大陸人</span></span>，獲得佢地既支持！！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中共最驚既絕對係反共思維係內地得以延續</span></span><br />\n最後，品蔥是個好東西<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（但係大家瀏覽要小心，舊品蔥已經被中共收左皮，已經無幾多可以比清醒人士呼吸自由空氣既平台）"},{"pid":"c89a7b8e263d4a866346ddaa6cd1e958a6b61d7b","tid":1473826,"uid":124616,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:19:15.000Z","msg":"大你老母陸 同你老母胞"},{"pid":"82141c4695b9ec4553561d640a4c2095441763de","tid